Document.name: Kerala Theater List
Document.description:
This list contains the locations of theaters in Kerala, along with links to online booking sites and information about the screens, such as their capacity, auditorium specifications, offline ticket prices, and contact details. If available, the history of the theater is also included.
Thanks to Google Local Guides for providing these informations.
